  "coverage_strategy": [
    "Encourage forward motion in clear paths.",
    "Upon obstacle detection, rotate systematically (prefer one direction per sweep).",
    "Introduce 'sweep_left' and 'sweep_right' to maintain consistent coverage direction, reducing oscillation.",
    "If surrounded or blocked (obs_front with no path_clear), use full_rotate to escape local minima.",
    "Switch between sweeping directions if needed, but avoid random walks.",
